{"tid":1976460,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"香港疫情好咗好多，會唔會多返招聘?","createTime":"2020-04-17T09:07:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T15:17:09.000Z","uid":152224,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1866567ffc8af438dc600f3dacded702669462c0","tid":1976460,"uid":152224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:07:00.000Z","msg":"屋企人、朋友、識嘅人 都係失業居多<br />\n自己係fg 搵工都搵到勁頹<br />\n<br />\n其實香港疫情已經好咗好多 (相比美國、歐洲)<br />\n連續6日單位數確診，得4個人死 (長者)，9個人危殆/嚴重<br />\n出街消費食飯嘅人多返好多<br />\n<br />\n公司應該開始請返人啦? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c1781994b0cb8da558d54fb059f57af3afd0af0","tid":1976460,"uid":12628,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:10:01.000Z","msg":"連登基本標準<br />\nFg 入職要有50k, <br />\n做二三年野，轉一轉人工要跳到50%以上<br />\n5～7年要升到上聿上管理層<br />\n做左十年，成為社會賢達！<br />\n如果咁都做唔到，建議該人士delete account"},{"pid":"db3ef525f72ff08a8ad2c252f354cff7d393c400","tid":1976460,"uid":119006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:29:00.000Z","msg":"起碼年尾"},{"pid":"6b4d06d4b7f47e986bab5553cb45fa916c203fe4","tid":1976460,"uid":152224,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"db3ef525f72ff08a8ad2c252f354cff7d393c400","tid":1976460,"uid":119006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:29:00.000Z","msg":"起碼年尾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T10:50:25.000Z","msg":"6月得唔得，唔想完final exam 冇野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (旅行又唔去得)"},{"pid":"3d71769df1a9333c5551d71d66658a901f61825b","tid":1976460,"uid":216704,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T10:54:26.000Z","msg":"其實都好睇其他國家<br />\n其他國家唔好 香港都好難好"},{"pid":"250aced989f6dcfb86e93dc46bac77b17ebd2fe9","tid":1976460,"uid":73991,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T11:10:11.000Z","msg":"呢排失業既係做邊行？我身邊啲人完全冇影響喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ac26398e3c3339093696a43f